  "prompt": "Complete the sentence with the correct past perfect simple form of \"already / see\": Steve ___ the film, so he didn't come with us to the cinema.",
  "explanation": "\"Already\" signals a completed action before another past event (not coming to the cinema), so use the past perfect simple: had already seen.",
